videos.description: LeBron James and Kevin Love each record double-doubles as the Cavs defeat the Grizzlies 116-111 for their 11th straight victory.
videos.headline: LeBron, Love fuel Cavs to 11th straight win

videos.description: LeBron James says that he's happy to have teammates that allow him to do what he does best and jokes that he's not motivated by an 11-game win streak because he's had a 27-game streak before.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (LeBron jokes about win streaks) 2017/12/2

videos.headline: LeBron jokes about win streaks
